name: Feast of Truffle Steak Dinner
description: Meal Feast: Double-click to set out a Feast of Truffle Steak Dinner to share with anyone in the area. Feast stays active for 5 minutes.

name: Deldrimor Steel Ingot
description: Refined from iron, steel, darksteel, and mithrillium.

name: Elonian Trouser Padding
description: Used to craft Elonian Leather Leggings.

name: Satchel of Carrion Winged Armor
description: Double-click to unpack a full set of level 65 armor.

name: Giver's Intricate Gossamer Insignia
description: Used in the crafting of armor with +Toughness, +Healing Power, and +Concentration.

name: Pot of Potato and Leek Soup
description: Soup Feast: Double-click to set out a Pot of Potato and Leek Soup to share with anyone in the area. Pot stays active for 5 minutes.

name: Mini Steam Minotaur
description: Double-click to summon this miniature to follow you around. Only one miniature may be in use at a time.

name: Satchel of Vital Embroidered Armor
description: Double-click to unpack a full set of level 10 armor.

name: Recipe: Satchel of Vigorous Student Armor (Master)
description: Double-click to learn the Tailor recipe for Satchel of Vigorous Masquerade Armor (Master)

name: Feast of Spiced Mashed Yams
description: Snack Feast: Double-click to set out a Feast of Spiced Mashed Yams to share with anyone in the area. Feast stays active for 5 minutes.

name: 20 Slot Oiled Pack
description: 20 Slots. If possible, junk items will fill this pack before other empty spaces. The contents of this pack will not move when inventory is sorted.

name: 20 Slot Invisible Pack
description: 20 Slots. Items in this pack will never appear in a sell-to-vendor list and will not move when inventory is sorted.
